10 Section 2. Section 61-3-406, MCA, is amended to read:
11 "61-3-406. Fees for personalized plates -- disposition. (1) In addition to all other fees and taxes
12 imposed by law, the applicant for a personalized license plate shall pay a fee of $25 $30 for the original
13 personalized license plate and a fee of $10 for each transfer or renewal of the personalized license plate.
14 (2) The revenue derived from the fee must be deposited in the state general fund Montana
15 highway patrol officers' retirement system pension fund until the closed highway patrol officers' retirement
16 system defined benefit plan is fully paid off. When the defined benefit plan is fully paid off, the revenue derived
17 from the fee must be deposited in the state general fund."
